window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Rule number one for the team owner’s daughter? </b><b><i>Don’t date the players.</i></b></p> <p>Especially not hotheaded tight ends with tattoos and impulse-control problems.</p> <p>That’s why Dominic Walker is completely off my radar. Sort of.</p> <p>Babysitting the team troublemaker when he’s forced to volunteer for the foundation where I work means I can’t exactly avoid him.</p> <p>I wish I had though. Because once I get to know Dominic, it’s almost impossible to ignore the feelings he brings out in me.</p> <p>Pretty soon, I’m breaking all my rules. I just have to hope he doesn’t break my heart in the process.</p>"; 
